# Get Customer Information
  This is the api documentation for the customer information.

## Create an customer
```shell
curl --location --request POST 'http://localhost:8091/data/v1/progressive/start' \
--header 'Authorization: asdfghjkl...' \
--data-raw '{
    "firstName": "Joe",
    "lastName": "Emison",
    "city": "Brooklyn",
    "state": "NY",
    "zip": "12344-56767",
    "address1": "1920 Edgemont Rd",
    "dateOfBirth": "02/13/1990",
    "email": "test@heykangaroo.com",
    "phone": "+1-202-460-3525",
    "isPremiumSubscriber": true,
    "connectedHome": {
        "moisture": "1",
        "theft": "6",
        "smoke": "2",
        "motion": "1",
        "waterShutoff": "0"
    }
}'
```
```ruby
